summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Water Department; accepting deeds to certain portions of the Plat of Fairwood Park Div. No. 9, a portion of the Plat of Fairwood Park Div. No. 14, and an unplatted portion of the Northwest quarter of the Northwest Quarter of Section 27, Township 23 North, Range 5 East, W.M., in King County, Washington, for water supply purposes and placing such properties under the jurisdiction of the Water Department.
